<p>Welcome to the <i>ToGI Chatroom of Discord</i>. It was created by Chinese Dragon to promote communication between our members.
The first thing you should do is visit the rules.
The general chat is meant to be used for conversations that don't really pertain to the site.
The plot chat is for discussing plots.
In the thread chat, you can post threads to alert others of their presence. If it is an open thread, make sure to use the @everyone tag.
Suggestions are for, well, suggestions.
If you have in questions, make sure you mention them in the questions chat.
Finally, like to spam? Well please keep it all in the spam chat.</p>
